        <p id="Par35">Sequence inconsistencies may lead to additional IP-TP combinations that satisfy the above conditions and could thus be used for the path completion of the considered candidate. In this case, the routine selects the pair of IP-TP combinations and, thereby, completes paths <inline-formula id="IEq215"><alternatives><tex-math id="M429">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
