        <p id="Par37">To assess the similarity between the subsequences, we employ a banded local sequence alignment with affine gap costs (cf. Additional file <xref rid="MOESM1" ref-type="media">1</xref>: Section <italic>Local sequence alignments</italic> for parameter settings) and accept alignments below a specified <italic>E</italic>-value threshold where at least <inline-formula id="IEq227"><alternatives><tex-math id="M453">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
