      <p id="Par49">Therefore, to identify IBs, the graph is searched for pairs of broken bulges, creating a set of candidates. In contrast to the toy example, the gene content is generally not perfectly conserved. The IBs are hence not necessarily of the same size. To account for this, a small relative deviation of<disp-formula id="Equ1"><alternatives><tex-math id="M713">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
