      <p id="Par50">The thus obtained sequence segments are subsequently examined for homology using a global sequence alignment. Candidates with alignment scores <italic>a</italic>, so that<disp-formula id="Equ2"><alternatives><tex-math id="M721">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
