    <sec id="Sec7">
      <title>Determination of the (<italic>k</italic> + 1)-mer size</title>
      <p id="Par51">The probably most important parameter that must be set at the beginning of the proposed approach is the <inline-formula id="IEq363"><alternatives><tex-math id="M727">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
