				\begin{document}$$r_{\text{sub}}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M922"><mml:msub><mml:mi>r</mml:mi><mml:mtext>sub</mml:mtext></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2023_5371_Article_IEq460.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>, and on the number of putative breakpoints <inline-formula id="IEq461"><alternatives><tex-math id="M923">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
