      <p id="Par67">To also visually assess the quality of the predicted breakpoint locations in the context of the MITOS2 gene annotations, a plot referred to as <italic>breakpoint plot</italic> was designed, showing which areas of the genomes are involved in a predicted breakpoint with respect to the gene annotations. Figure <xref rid="Fig10" ref-type="fig">10</xref> illustrates how to interpret this plot with a simple example.</p>
