        <p id="Par71">The two Decapodiformes of the second case study feature an exceptionally high number of 52 putative breakpoints (cf. Table <xref rid="Tab3" ref-type="table">3</xref>), of which DeBBI detects the great majority with <inline-formula id="IEq441"><alternatives><tex-math id="M883">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
