        <p id="Par80">We find that running times depend both on the level of sequence inconsistencies, as controlled by <inline-formula id="IEq460"><alternatives><tex-math id="M921">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
